title: Reactions of U(DMSO)<sub>8</sub>(ClO<sub>4</sub>)<sub>4</sub> with Terpyridine Yield Dimeric Hydrolysis Products and Induce C-C Coupling: Dataset
description: This dataset collects the inputs and outputs of the calculations (Gaussian, ADF, NBO, QTAIM) discussed in the paper entitled "Reactions of U(DMSO)<sub>8</sub>(ClO<sub>4</sub>)<sub>4</sub> with Terpyridine Yield Dimeric Hydrolysis Products and Induce C-C Coupling" by Emily R. Mikeska, Richard E. Wilson, and Valérie Vallet.
